The manner in which African countries have managed the coronavirus pandemic has set an example for the rest of the world. That was the message of United Nations Secretary General António Guterres in an exclusive interview with SABCNEWS in New York on the global organisation’s release of a policy brief on COVID-19 in Africa. For more news, visit sabcnews.com and also #SABCNews, #Coronavirus, #COVID19 on Social Media. 